data.title: The Bill actor Roberta Taylor dies at 76 after a tragic fall that caused health issues
data.meta_description: The beloved British television actress Roberta Taylor, known for her memorable roles in The Bill and EastEnders, has passed away at the age of 76. Her death comes after a prolonged struggle with health issues following a tragic fall. Roberta's passing marks the end of an era for her fans and the television industry.
data.text:
The beloved British television actress Roberta Taylor, known for her memorable roles in The Bill and EastEnders, has passed away at the age of 76. Her death comes after a prolonged struggle with health issues following a tragic fall. Roberta's passing marks the end of an era for her fans and the television industry.

July 24, 2024 / 14:46 IST
